headline: Is Target Attractively Priced After 33% Fall and Supply Chain Concerns in 2025?
summary: Wondering whether Target is attractively priced right now? You are not alone, and digging into valuation could help you spot an opportunity before the market catches on. The company has moved 3.3% higher over the past month, but shares are still down more than 33% year-to-date, signaling shifting investor sentiment and possible changes in risk perception.
